      <p begin="00:00:14.800" end="00:00:18.067">CHRISTIAN MEULI: I saw the cityin the deep, deep distance,</p>
      <p begin="00:00:18.133" end="00:00:20.567">that was dark green, and allthese lights flickering</p>
      <p begin="00:00:20.633" end="00:00:22.667">and clouds flowing over it.</p>
      <p begin="00:00:22.733" end="00:00:25.733">And this all started aftertremendous geometric patterns</p>
      <p begin="00:00:25.800" end="00:00:29.867">that are incredibly rapid thatyou can't describe to anybody,</p>
      <p begin="00:00:29.933" end="00:00:31.767">they're so fast.</p>
      <p begin="00:00:31.833" end="00:00:32.633">After those had slowed down,</p>
      <p begin="00:00:32.700" end="00:00:35.833">I saw this city in thedeep distance.</p>
