      <p begin="00:01:10.167" end="00:01:12.367">and she said "What elsedo you want?"</p>
      <p begin="00:01:12.433" end="00:01:16.667">And I said, "What elsedo you have?"</p>
      <p begin="00:01:33.667" end="00:01:38.533">JOE ROGAN: This is the storyof DMT, or dimethyltryptamine.</p>
